          "treatment": "Analgesia (NSAIDs first-line: diclofenac 75 mg IM/PO, ketorolac). Tamsulosin 0.4 mg daily for MET. Hydration. Strain urine to catch stone. Monitor weekly x 4-6 weeks. If not passed by 4 weeks: reimage."
